reviewText: Grandkids love watching and they are getting quality entertainment!
Got a great deal on a used copy of this.  Alot of bang for your buck.  Six DVDs, each 28 minutes long.  One CD of activities, which we did not use.  Highly recommend.

My 2 year old recieved these for Christmas, and absolutely LOVES them. The voices aren't annoying, it's not too cheesy, and the story lines/lessons are great for her to grow with. Heck, she is even loving watching it to potty train, woohoo! Hoping to buy more! Very thankful for this show.
Excellent Service and Quality Product at the right price - thanks!
I wish this had caught on and stayed on.  We love this show!
My girls love these videos.  Great price!
